summary: What if iron man is in all the new phase 4 movies (recently confirmed that he’s in captain marvel) because he’s going to die in...
body:
What if iron man is in all the new phase 4 movies (recently confirmed that he’s in captain marvel) because he’s going to die in Endgame.

They’re trying to put in as many cute, heartfelt, and important scenes of tony so we don’t think he’s gonna die.

Logically, we’re gonna think that “oh Tony is involved with carol, somehow he’s gonna help her grow as the new Captain, so Steve is gonna most likely die” or that he’ll become the director of shield (another theory most have brought up)

But no. They’re trying to trick us, all these suprise additional scenes with Tony is to make the blow of his death even more heartbreaking by misleading us.
